Ansible config to install idp-3.2 on IDP clusters

Target site needs some setup before first install
-------------------------------------------------

(as root, on target)
# ./system-setup.sh


--------------------------------------------------

To install or upgrade the idp or the gateway

2) ./install.sh [ idp | gateway ]  [ idp_eval | idp_prod ]

idp_eval = idpeval01
idp_prod = idp01, idp02

